To update to a newer version of puppet-hiera:


# Add the new remote if you dont already have it
git add remote puppetlabs-hiera git://github.com/puppetlabs/hiera-puppet.git

# Fetch new commits (DON'T CHECKOUT OR PULL)
git fetch puppetlabs-hiera

# For checking out a specific version:
git checkout v0.3.0 lib/
git commit -m 'Checkout out v0.3.0 of upstream puppet-hiera'

# done ;)
